tedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T07:36:31.000Z","msg":"rx100m5rx100m5 好似無touch screen focus<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n腰平, 街拍揾到目標, 點一點個screen focus + tracking...........<br />\n<br />\n等行得夠近(要wide angle),啱先㩒shutter, 同partner一路傾 一路拍, so easy, <br />\n<br />\n 目標和你距離一路變化, 仲hyperfocal?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm1.staticflickr.com/424/32641082526_e7a05cd41b_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm1.staticflickr.com%2F424%2F32641082526_e7a05cd41b_o.jpg&h=21ad2755&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T16:58:04.000Z","msg":"用得hyperfocus 就唔會理目標距離嘅變化<br />\napsc為例, f5.6 focus at 1.5m, 對焦範圍係1-3m, 已經夠一般snapshot 用<br />\n按快門個下只需要理構圖出黎大約咩樣, 其他嘢根本唔使理<br />\n再者snapshot 表達到就夠, 係咪要100%中焦真係見人見志<br />\n<br />\n不過rx100系列的確係好機, 唔知今年肯唔肯加番個touch screen 同減價未<br />\n再唔係rx1都係時候加番 4k 出mk3 <br />\nlx100 出左 4年, 但m4/3好似冇乜新嘢加到落去<br />\n想換機都唔知換咩好"},{"pid":"b4d7e73711ea81977ab85b2ea683b9a7c7b5a908","tid":623480,"uid":9412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T17:45:18.000Z","msg":"邊到可以買到好既gr？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0f5f9c25384609c33551cbbf525598db6ed9d65","tid":623480,"uid":63515,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b4d7e73711ea81977ab85b2ea683b9a7c7b5a908","tid":623480,"uid":9412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T17:45:18.000Z","msg":"邊到可以買到好既gr？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T17:55:58.000Z","msg":"咪鬼買，1萬快門都唔夠就有問題<br />\n<br />\n好多人都係咁"},{"pid":"9e71e40c6950dfacf7d0f5fb4366b11f2b825d3c","tid":623480,"uid":19363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T10:45:36.000Z","msg":"lx10, zs200"},{"pid":"581110cf30dffe71088b66a4d2335c8eba6b01de","tid":623480,"uid":60136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4d7e73711ea81977ab85b2ea683b9a7c7b5a908","tid":623480,"uid":